generated_sparql:
PREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?type (COUNT(?entity) AS ?count) WHERE {
  ?entity a ?type .
  ?type rdfs:subClassOf* brick:Point .
}
GROUP BY ?type
ORDER BY DESC(?count)
